itable\" style=\"width:80%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:20%;\"|'''Figure'''\n! style=\"width:30%;\"|'''Accessories'''\n! style=\"width:30%;\"|'''Description'''\n|-\n|Captain America\n|Shield\n|Re-released figure from the Mandroid BAF Series\n|-\n|[[Iron Man (comics)|Iron Man]]\n|Alternate unmasked head\n|Redeco of the Bleeding Edge Iron Man figure from the Iron Monger BAF Series\n|-\n|[[Thor (Marvel Comics)|Thor]]\n|Mjolnir\n|Re-released figure from the Terrax BAF Series\n|-\n|Hulk\n|\n|Re-released figure from the Toys \"R\" Us two-pack with Valkyrie\n|-\n|[[Ultron]]\n|\n|Redeco of Ultron figure from the Iron Monger BAF Series\n|}\n\n===EntertainmentEarth.com===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n!width=10%|'''Set'''\n!width=5%|'''Release'''\n!width=20%|'''Figure'''\n!width=40%|'''Accessories'''\n!width=40%|'''Description'''\n|-\n|rowspan=5|Guardians of the Galaxy Box Set ([[Earth-616]])\n|rowspan=5|2015\n|[[Groot]]\n|Baby Groot in pot\n|\n|-\n|[[Drax the Destroyer]]\n|Cosmic Cube, 4 Daggers and Interchangeable Hands\n|\n|-\n|[[Gamora]]\n|alternate head, Cloak and Sword\n|\n|-\n|[[Star-Lord]] (Peter Quill)\n|2 Blasters\n|\n|-\n|[[Rocket Raccoon]]\n|3 Blasters\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[Avengers: Infinity War]]\n|rowspan=2|2018\n|[[Scarlet Witch]]\n|Energy effects\n|Repaint of the Abomination wave figure\n|-\n|[[Vision (Marvel Comics)|Vision]]\n|Alternate hands\n|Exclusive\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[Secret Empire (comic book)|Secret Empire]]\n|rowspan=2|2018\n|Captain America\n|Shield\n|[[Captain America#Alternate timeline Hydra duplicate|Supreme Leader]] version<br />Exclusive\n|-\n|[[Arnim Zola]]\n|\n|Modern version<br />Exclusive\n|}\n\n===GameStop===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:80%;\"\n|-\n!width=20%|'''Figure'''\n!width=40%|'''Accessories'''\n!width=40%|'''Description'''\n|-\n|[[Deadpool]]\n|Tendrils, twin energy katanas and alternate head and hands\n|\"Back in Black\" [[Venom (Marvel Comics character)|Venom Symbiote]] version\n|-\n|[[Spider-Man (Insomniac Games)|Spider-Man]]\n|Web line and alternate hands\n|[[Spider-Man (2018 video game)]] version\n|-\n|[[Ultron]]\n|\n|[[Avengers: Age of Ultron]] version<br />Repaint of the Ultron BAF\n|-\n|[[Hulk]]\n|Alternate head and hands\n|[[Avengers (2020 video game)]] Outback version\n|}\n\n===HasbroToyShop.com (2008)===\nHasbro has a long tradition of doing \"Fans' Choice\" figures for their Star Wars license, but this is their first shot for Marvel Legends. In a poll run through ToyFare magazine, fans could pick which of eight Marvel characters they'd want to see as an exclusive, and Sunfire beat out such luminaries as Silver Samurai and Gambit.<br />The figure is packaged on a unique blister card with a fiery backdrop and a large cardboard wrap around the bottom.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:80%;\"\n|-\n!width=20%|'''Figure'''\n!width=40%|'''Description'''\n|-\n|[[Sunfire (comics)#Horseman of Apocalypse|Sunfire]]\n|Age of Apocalypse version\n|}\n\n===HASCON===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:80%;\"\n|-\n!width=20%|'''Figure'''\n!width=40%|'''Accessories'''\n!width=40%|'''Description'''\n|-\n|[[Deadpool]]\n|Twin katanas\n|[[Uncanny X-Force]] version\n|}\n\n===Hasbro Pulse===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:80%;\"\n|-\n!width=20%|'''Figure'''\n!width=40%|'''Accessories'''\n!width=40%|'''Description'''\n|-\n|[[HYDRA (comics)|HYDRA]] Trooper\n|Rifle and pistol\n|Rerelease of the Mandroid wave HYDRA Soldier at a discounted price and with different accessories\n|}\n\n===Marvel Unlimited Online===\nFree with the purchase of a new [[Marvel Unlimited]] Plus digital comics subscription at Marvel.com.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n!width=10%| Figure\n!width=5%| Year\n!width=30%| Accessories\n!width=30%| Description\n!width=40%| Comic\n|-\n|[[Ultron]]\n|2013\n|Stand, personalized Plus Member card, welcome letter and custom collectible comic box\n|Gold repaint from the Iron Monger Series\n|''Age of Ultron'' #10 (variant edition) cover art by Sa