ost]]\n|\n|\n|Right arm and leg\n|-\n|[[Hercules (Marvel Comics)|Hercules]]\n|mace\n|\n|Left wing\n|-\n|Gladiator Hulk\n|shield and removable helmet\n|Originally shipped with an erroneous silver left arm, but this was later updated to the correct green one.<br />Retool of the [[Hulk Classics]] [[Horsemen of Apocalypse|War Hulk]] figure from ToyBiz with a new head and accessories.\n|Head\n|-\n|[[Ultimate Iron Man (character)|Ultimate Iron Man]]\n|\n|Packaged with helmet on or off\n|Torso\n|-\n|rowspan=12|[[Blob (comics)|Blob]]\n|rowspan=12|2007\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[Jean Grey]]\n|\n|[[X-Men: The Last Stand]] version\n|rowspan=2|Right arm\n|-\n|\n|Phoenix variant\n|-\n|[[Juggernaut (comics)|Juggernaut]]\n|helmet\n|[[X-Men: The Last Stand]] version\n|Hands\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[Quicksilver (comics)|Quicksilver]]\n|\n|Regular version\n|rowspan=2|Left arm\n|-\n|\n|First appearance (green) variant\n|-\n|[[She-Hulk]]\n|\n|\n|Upper torso\n|-\n|[[Thor (Marvel Comics)|Thor]]\n|Mjolnir and battle axe\n|Lord of Asgard version\n|Head\n|-\n|[[Ultimate Wolverine]]\n|\n|\n|Lower torso\n|-\n|[[Xorn]]\n|Helmet\n|\n|Left leg\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[Henry Pym|Yellowjacket]]\n|rowspan=2|\n|Regular version\n|rowspan=2|Right leg\n|-\n|Gold variant\n|-\n|rowspan=10|[[Brood (comics)|Brood Queen]]\n|rowspan=10|2007\n|[[Black Knight (Dane Whitman)]]\n|sword and shield\n|\n|legs, right\n|-\n|[[Bucky Barnes]]\n|\n|Golden Age version\n|Tail\n|-\n|Captain America\n|shield\n|Golden Age version\n|Legs, left\n|-\n|[[Colossus (comics)|Colossus]]\n|\n|[[X-Men: The Last Stand]] version\n|leg, right front\n|-\n|[[Cyclops (Marvel Comics)|Cyclops]]\n|\n|The Astonishing X-Men version\n|Head\n|-\n|[[Danger (comics)|Danger]]\n|\n|\n|Wings\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[Hydra (Marvel Comics)|Hydra Soldier]]\n|rowspan=2|guns\n|Closed mouth\n|rowspan=2|leg, left front\n|-\n|Open mouth<br />Retool of the cancelled ToyBiz Hydra Soldier pack-in figure that was originally scheduled to come with the Onslaught wave Loki\n|-\n|rowspan=2|Marvel 