usive\n|-\n|[[Vision (Marvel Comics)|Vision]]\n|\n|[[West Coast Avengers]] version<br>White repaint of Hulkbuster BAF series Vision\n|-\n|rowspan=2|Captain America: Civil War\n|rowspan=2|2016\n|[[War Machine]]\n|Stun baton, mini-guns and alternate hands\n|[[Captain America: Civil War]] (Mark III) version<br />Exclusive\n|-\n|[[Iron Man (comics)|Iron Man]]\n|Shoulder-mounted machine gun\n|[[Iron Man 3]] Mark XXVII (Disco) Armor version<br />Repaint of the MCU Iron Patriot figure from the Iron Monger BAF Series\n|-\n|rowspan=2|Thor: Ragnarok\n|rowspan=2|2017\n|[[Thor (Marvel Comics)|Thor]]\n|Sword, lightning effect and interchangeable hands\n|[[Thor: Ragnarok]] version<br />Retool of the Gladiator Hulk wave Thor with a new head\n|-\n|[[Valkyrie (Marvel Comics)|Valkyrie]]\n|Dragonfang sword and scabbard\n|[[Thor: Ragnarok]] version<br />Exclusive\n|-\n|rowspan=2|Black Panther\n|rowspan=2|2018\n|[[Erik Killmonger]]\n|Sword, spear and alternate unmasked head\n|[[Black Panther (film)]] Vibranium suit version<br />Retool of the Okoye wave Erik Killmonger with a new head\n|-\n|[[Everett Ross]]\n|Handgun\n|[[Black Panther (film)]] version<br />Exclusive\n|-\n|rowspan=2|Avengers: Infinity War\n|rowspan=2|2018\n|[[Falcon (comics)|Falcon]]\n|Attachable wings, flight pack, assault rifle and Redwing drone\n|[[Avengers: Infinity War]] version<br />Repaint of the Walmart-exclusive Falcon\n|-\n|[[Bucky Barnes|Winter Soldier]]\n|Laser cannon\n|[[Avengers: Infinity War]] version<br />Exclusive\n|-\n|rowspan=2|Into the Spider-Verse\n|rowspan=2|2018\n|[[Spider-Man (Miles Morales)]]\n|Venom blast effect piece, alternate unmasked head and hands\n|[[Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse]] version<br />Redeco of the Space Knight Venom wave Miles Morales\n|-\n|[[Spider-Woman (Gwen Stacy)|Spider-Gwen]]\n|Alternate unmasked head and two web-lines\n|[[Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse]] version<br />Redeco of the Absorbing Man wave Spider-Gwen\n|-\n|rowspan=2|Spider-Man: Homecoming\n|rowspan=2|2019