omics)|HYDRA]] Soldier\n|Rifle, machine gun and alternate heads\n|Retool of the Mandroid series figure\n|-\n|HYDRA Enforcer\n|Rocket launcher, rifle, knife and alternate heads\n|Captain Britain head, Nuke body repaint<br />Exclusive\n|-\n|rowspan=2|Black Panther\n|rowspan=2|2018\n|[[Shuri (comics)|Black Panther (Shuri)]]\n|Vibranium spear\n|Exclusive\n|-\n|[[Klaw (comics)|Klaw]]\n|Sonic energy effect\n|Exclusive\n|}\n\n===Walgreens===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n!width=5%|Release\n!width=20%| Figure\n!width=40%| Accessories\n!width=40%| Description\n|-\n|2014\n|[[Flash Thompson|Agent Venom]]\n|Four guns and tendrils\n|Flash Thompson, as he first appeared in ''Secret Avengers'' (2010) #23\n|-\n|2015\n|[[Eric O'Grady#Black Ant|Black Ant]]\n|\n|Ant-Man's [[Life Model Decoy]]\n|-\n|2015\n|[[Daredevil (Marvel Comics character)|Daredevil]]\n|Billy clubs\n|First appearance yellow costume version\n|-\n|2016\n|[[Namor]]\n|Trident and alternate hands\n|Modern version\n|-\n|2016\n|[[Punisher]]\n|Alternate head, Two Guns and a Rocket Launcher\n|Jim Lee version\n|-\n|2017\n|[[Invisible Woman]] and [[H.E.R.B.I.E.]]\n|Alternate hand\n|\n|-\n|2017\n|[[Johnny Storm|Human Torch]]\n|Flame effects and alternate hands\n|\n|-\n|2017\n|[[Medusa (Marvel Comics)|Medusa]]\n|\n|Retool of Medusa from the Thanos Imperative box set\n|-\n|2018\n|[[Reed Richards|Mr. Fantastic]]\n|Alternate bendable arms, [[Ultimate Nullifier]]\n|\n|-\n|2018\n|[[Thing (comics)|The Thing]]\n|Alternate head and hands\n|\n|-\n|2018\n|[[Silver Surfer]]\n|Surfboard, power cosmic effects and four alternate hands\n|\n|-\n|2018\n|[[Magik (Illyana Rasputin)|Magik]]\n|2 swords, alternate hand, 3 magic effects, flaming skull and Lockheed\n|Modern version<br />Rerelease of the Magik figure from the SDCC-exclusive Book of the Vishanti set\n|-\n|2019\n|[[Mystique (comics)|Mystique]]\n|Pistol, laser rifle, and alternate Rogue and [[Lilandra]] heads\n|Classic version\n|-\n|2019\n|[[Doctor Doom]]\n|Alternate 